{"type":"message","id":"78d128da","parentId":"a219c2aa","timestamp":"2026-04-07T00:00:00.079Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:da4546e3-8bdd-4291-b88f-472a4b5d4b34 盘前选股+生成plan+上传] 执行每日盘前流程：\n\n第一步：检查今天是否为交易日\n- 如果是周末或法定节假日（清明节4/4-4/6、劳动节5/1-5/5、端午节6/19-6/21、国庆10/1-10/7等），直接输出\"今日休市，跳过盘前任务\"并结束\n- 2026年工作日休市日：20260101 20260102 20260216 20260217 20260218 20260219 20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001 20261002 20261005 20261006 20261007\n\n第二步：确定今天日期\n- 运行 date +%Y%m%d 获取今天的 YYYYMMDD 格式日期\n- 用这个日期作为 preopen 的 --date 参数\n\n第三步：跑 preopen 选股\n- cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && nohup /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen --date YYYYMMDD > /tmp/preopen_YYYYMMDD.log 2>&1 &\n- 等待完成（约30-60秒），检查 /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant/outputs/preopen/YYYYMMDD/ 目录下文件是否齐全\n\n第四步：读取选股结果\n- top_y5.csv（候选股票+因子分数）\n- market_regime.json（市场状态）\n\n第五步：用 Tushare 查候选股前一日收盘价（不要用Baostock）\n- 通过 sys.path.insert + _get_token() 获取 token\n- max_price = 前收盘价 × 1.02\n\n第六步：搜新闻（Tavily）\n- 搜索隔夜美股、中东战争、大宗商品等宏观新闻\n- 生成 market_context.json，对候选股加权重排\n\n第七步：生成 plan.json 并校验（关键！）\n- action 必须是 BUY_ALLOWED 或 SELL_ALL，绝对不能是 None 或 buy\n- buy 数组至少有1只股票\n- 每只股票必须有 code(6位数字), name, volume(手数), max_price(前收×1.02), stop_loss_pct, take_profit_pct, reason\n- max_price 必须是合理的实际股价范围（不能是个位数或超过10000）\n\n第八步：上传到云服务器\n- 用 paramiko SCP 上传到 E:/Quant/strategies/plan.json\n- 上传后读回验证 action 和 buy 内容正确\n\n注意：\n- 账户 68039812（模拟盘），资金限制10万，单只不超过20%\n- 昨日涨停/接近涨跌停（±8%以上）的股票降低权重但不排除\n- 数据源优先级：Tushare(主力) > Baostock(备选)\n- SSH 密码从 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 的 env.SSH_PASSWORD 读取\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 — 08:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-07 00:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775520000078}}
{"type":"message","id":"2187a51e","parentId":"78d128da","timestamp":"2026-04-07T00:01:06.666Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nI need to execute the daily pre-market workflow according to the cron job. Let me break this down:\n\n1. First, I need to check if today is a trading day\n2. Get today's date in YYYYMMDD format\n3. Run the preopen stock selection\n4. Read the results\n5. Use Tushare to get previous day's closing prices\n6. Search news using Tavily\n7. Generate plan.json with proper validation\n8. Upload to cloud server\n\nLet me start by checking if today is a trading day. The date is 2026-04-07. Looking at the provided holidays:\n- 20260406 (April 6) is listed as a holiday, but April 7 is not\n- So April 7, 2026 should be a trading day\n\nLet me get the current date first, then proceed with the steps.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<thinking>\nI need to execute the daily pre-market workflow. Let me start by checking if today is a trading day and get the current date.\n\nThe current time shows Tuesday, April 7th, 2026. Looking at the holidays list:\n- 20260406 (April 6) is listed as a holiday\n- But April 7, 2026 is not in the holiday list, so it should be a trading day\n\nLet me start by getting today's date and then proceed with the workflow.\n</thinking>\n\nI'll execute the daily pre-market workflow now. Let me start by checking if today is a trading day and getting the current date.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5269aab48c024ffead977140","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"date +%Y%m%d"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":40807,"output":342,"cacheRead":1300,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42449,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775520000079}}
