{"type":"message","id":"a6a8771c","parentId":"097f3047","timestamp":"2026-04-07T00:01:28.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nGood, today's date is 20260407. Now let me check if this is a trading day. Looking at the holidays list:\n\n20260101, 20260102, 20260216, 20260217, 20260218, 20260219, 20260223, 20260406, 20260501, 20260504, 20260505, 20260619, 20260925, 20261001, 20261002, 20261005, 20261006, 20261007\n\n20260407 is not in the list, so it's a trading day. Now I need to proceed with the preopen stock selection.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n今天是交易日（20260407），开始执行盘前流程。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_af82b804fa684cf5870471fd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && nohup /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen --date 20260407 > /tmp/preopen_20260407.log 2>&1 &"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":11,"output":252,"cacheRead":42448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42711,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775520066691}}
